                        "text": [
                            "A being of great power. He wreaks a path of devastation upon any land that he visits.",
                            "He attacked Knork, the capitol of Kolis, where the party had just awoken in the hospital. He summoned an ogre warrior and a mysterious young man to help him attack the city. He has not been seen since this attack."
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
